dc_title_s: Frontenac Arch Biosphere Reserve (FABR) Stewardship Projects, 2002-2014
dc_description_s:
This dataset aims to centralize information about stewardship projects in the Fron tenac Arch Biosphere Reserve (FABR) since its designation in 2002 until the present (2014), for the purpose of the UNESCO 10 year Periodic Review. This data may be modified as information is updated and added.
The dataset was created as part of course requirements for ENSC430.
